The car is Peter Forsgård old.
Henrik Gustafson is the person who stands up longest to the right.
Johan and Jimmy Eriksson (brother) is in the car. Johan cames up trow the top.
Jimmy trow the sidewindow.

@{b}Level 2@{ub}
